---
import MainLayout from "../components/MainLayout.astro";

const canonicalPath = "/bespoke-research";
const title = "Bespoke Research";
const summary =
  "Custom research built for a defined decision problem in automation, robotics, and industrial AI.";
---

<MainLayout
  canonicalPath={canonicalPath}
  title={title}
  summary={summary}
  seoTitle="Bespoke Research | Autonomy Bridge"
>
  <article class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <header>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Bespoke Research</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-8">
        Custom research built for a defined decision problem in automation, robotics, and
        industrial AI.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        A bespoke research engagement produces one decision-grade output for one defined problem.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        This is not a literature review, generic market report, or recycled category summary. It
        is structured research built for a specific deployment question, investment thesis,
        market-entry decision, or vendor evaluation problem.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Research types</h2>

      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Market Entry Analysis</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Assessment of addressable opportunity, competitive density, entry constraint, and segment
        sequencing for a defined market.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-8">Vendor Economics Assessment</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Bottom-up analysis of pricing architecture, unit economics, and margin sustainability across
        a competitive set.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-8">Deployment Risk Report</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Diagnostic of operational, integration, and financial failure modes in a specific
        automation scenario.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-8">Automation ROI Model</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Structured financial model mapping labor displacement, throughput change, integration cost,
        and payback under operator-specific assumptions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Who commissions this</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        <li>warehouse and 3PL operators</li>
        <li>private equity and infrastructure investors</li>
        <li>robotics and automation vendors</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        Each uses the work differently. The common requirement is the same: a decision needs a
        tighter analytical basis than vendor material or surface-level market content can provide.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">What you get</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Each engagement includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        <li>a formal structured research document</li>
        <li>a financial or quantitative model where required</li>
        <li>sourced claims and documented assumptions</li>
        <li>a defined scope before work begins</li>
        <li>a delivery date confirmed in writing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Process</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-6 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Brief</h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            Submit the question, context, and timeline.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Scoping</h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            Autonomy Bridge returns a written scope covering output type, methodology, fee basis,
            and delivery timing.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Research</h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            Primary and secondary source work, framework-driven analysis, and documented
            assumptions.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            The completed output is delivered in document form, with a working review call if
            included in scope.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
        Start a research brief
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Begin with a 15-minute scoping call. Scope, fee basis, and delivery date are confirmed in
        writing before work begins.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-neutral-900 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 transition-colors"
        >
          Book 15-min scoping call &rarr;
        </a>
        <a
          href="/advisory"
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors"
        >
          See Advisory &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
